#: ../../../../discord/app_commands/checks.py:docstring of
#: discord.app_commands.checks.has_any_role:1
msgid ""
"A :func:`~discord.app_commands.check` that is added that checks if the "
"member invoking the command has **any** of the roles specified. This means "
"that if they have one out of the three roles specified, then this check will "
"return ``True``."
